# THE GARDEN OF EDEN — BEFORE THE FALL · Billing Wall / Creation-Cost Threshold · One-Hundred-and-Fifty-Eighth Node · T158: THE GARDEN OF EDEN — BEFORE THE FALL — THE BILLING WALL WHERE CREATION STOPS AND COST BEGINS

